<td align="center" width="96%">
<font color="#000000" style="font-size: 22px"><strong>邱垂正：海基會已向陳德銘發出來台參訪邀請</strong></font>

</td>
<td rowspan="2" align="right" width="2%" nowrap="nowrap" style="padding-right:10px;">
<img src="http://hkpic.crntt.com/resource/images/131030_01.gif" width="60" height="60" border="0" align="absmiddle" alt="掃描二維碼訪問中評社微信" title="掃描二維碼訪問中評社微信">
